WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:16.500 --> 00:00:19.250
Now you know it anyway

00:00:43.375 --> 00:00:45.791
Good morning.
- Good morning.

00:00:46.500 --> 00:00:49.166
You sell... stories?

00:00:50.125 --> 00:00:51.917
What are your stories about?

00:00:52.041 --> 00:00:54.979
Well, this one is about an elephant...

00:00:55.081 --> 00:00:58.125
...and this one is about a helicopter...

00:00:58.250 --> 00:01:01.375
...and this one is about a mean fox...

00:01:01.542 --> 00:01:03.750
Oh, what happens in that story?

00:01:03.917 --> 00:01:05.708
In this one?

00:01:07.667 --> 00:01:10.667
Well, once upon a time
there was a fox...

00:01:11.000 --> 00:01:12.875
...who was very smart.

00:01:13.000 --> 00:01:16.875
Because he'd read all the books
in the book tree.

00:01:17.000 --> 00:01:19.583
But the fox was also very mean.

00:01:19.750 --> 00:01:23.875
Because the rabbits
and the elephant and...

00:01:24.792 --> 00:01:27.667
...and the hedgehog and the bear...

00:01:27.833 --> 00:01:31.708
...weren't allowed to read in the tree
by the fox.

00:01:31.875 --> 00:01:35.292
He was afraid
that all the other animals...

00:01:35.458 --> 00:01:37.625
...would become just as smart.

00:01:37.917 --> 00:01:42.333
But the girl rabbit wanted to know
where rabbits come from.

00:01:43.250 --> 00:01:47.458
And then she sneaked up the tree
to read about everything.

00:01:48.583 --> 00:01:52.875
The fox found out! He went to the tree
with his stupid friends.

00:01:53.000 --> 00:01:54.458
They grabbed the rabbit.

00:01:55.000 --> 00:01:57.542
The other animals didn't think
that was fair.

00:01:57.708 --> 00:02:00.417
They went to the fox
who got very scared...

00:02:00.583 --> 00:02:02.333
...and let go of the rabbit.

00:02:02.500 --> 00:02:05.625
They pushed against the tree
that shook and creaked...

00:02:05.792 --> 00:02:07.000
...and fell...

00:02:09.875 --> 00:02:11.375
Right on top of the fox.

00:02:12.792 --> 00:02:14.500
What's the price?

00:02:15.750 --> 00:02:18.000
I don't really know.

00:02:18.167 --> 00:02:19.917
Now you know the story anyway.

